{"tid":105112,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟人死左之後會點","createTime":"2017-02-02T15:39:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T17:57:47.000Z","uid":34067,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b443c635e8c52b81996805eaad41ac24ee05263","tid":105112,"uid":34067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T15:39:16.000Z","msg":"作為一個成日亂諗野既人<br />\n成日都會突然間諗起究竟人死左會點<br />\n我完全明白點解古代皇帝唔想死而要搞呢樣嗰樣求長生不死<br />\n我成日都會係到諗<br />\n人死後既意識會點<br />\n係咪世界上就唔會再有&quot;我&quot;既存在<br />\n我完全冇辦法想像會係點<br />\n更甚既係<br />\n有時我會諗萬一人類死晒又會係點<br />\n咁係咪自此就會冇晒&quot;人類&quot;呢個種族<br />\n冇左人類呢個種族<br />\n咁即使地球N種宗教信仰講既咩天堂輪迴轉世whatever<br />\n咁&quot;我&quot;都冇可能憑任何一種方法以其他形式再次成為人類<br />\n<br />\n我其實一諗到自己死左之後既世界已經覺得好驚<br />\n因為我好怕自己意識既消失<br />\n我已經唔會再係我<br />\n<br />\n當然我有向過身邊既人問過呢個問題<br />\n有宗教信仰既就會用返佢套信仰黎答我<br />\n冇既就會用佢既想像力諗下一世會點點點<br />\n但係呢樣始終解答唔到我既問題<br />\n<br />\n我相信呢隻世界都冇人解答到呢個問題<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999<br />\n純粹突然間諗到咩想打啲野分享下自己個心情"},{"pid":"12af5cc03e14c91a5011383c10d387db6d055291","tid":105112,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T15:39:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s17.postimg.org/rz672qrr3/56c9eb361e27c7617.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs17.postimg.org%2Frz672qrr3%2F56c9eb361e27c7617.gif&h=77b23013&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc68bac3d1c72d4f8add393a666c440c4d2dadac","tid":105112,"uid":7615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T16:41:27.000Z","msg":"肉體消失左 冇左意識<br />\n就唔會有以後 因為你都唔會有思考既能力<br />\n所謂宗教（大部分）都係想你仲生存緊既時候行多啲善<br />\n我不思故我不在<br />\n利申：好耐冇食藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28bdd8168199ed4749c3bddb369c2abd9b7e4a5d","tid":105112,"uid":72226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:38:03.000Z","msg":"人死如燈滅"},{"pid":"6080af93310bed4244a154c283b4ae2cf66e92af","tid":105112,"uid":15413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:47:03.000Z","msg":"試下咪知囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0613bf9c3d10f9f1fe440e04405ba412a0747c40","tid":105112,"uid":1346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:50:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下咪知囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b341602b7130403a11d84300e581ae549b8452cb","tid":105112,"uid":25357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:52:44.000Z","msg":"無，所有野都無曬"},{"pid":"690d340e50110c6114724c2ea91b070df4714f73","tid":105112,"uid":44741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:57:47.000Z","msg":"正所謂：塵歸塵，土歸土<br />\n最終你只會變成養份，冇所謂意識存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}